Sorry to hear you fainted man, it utterly sucks.


I've had it happen, the exact same way. It's a sugar crash, probably from just chugging Gatoraid all day, then your body burning through it in your sleep because your metabolism will be sky high.
It's happened to me twice (both times, taking a piss). I came to, straddling to the toilet with my head on the cistern the first time, then bent backwards over the side of the bath the second time. It's pretty scary but luckily I didn't injure myself, probably because my body basically rog-dolled. If you get some complex carbs/fruit and water in you afterwards and you're fine. Stay healthy and look after yourself dude!

snippet.textDisplay: What's up Sean. I had basically the same thing happen to me a few years back. I got up to take a piss while my wife was in the shower and after I finished I had that weird feeling like you mentioned,  minus the red and black spots... then I woke up with my hand in the toilet wondering what the hell just happened.
